Backtest 0.92. Live: -40%. Why?

2
00:00:03,200 --> 00:00:07,500
Sensitivity measurement —
which parameters actually move fitness?

3
00:00:07,800 --> 00:00:13,500
12 axes probed. 3 carry signal. 9 are decoys.

4
00:00:14,000 --> 00:00:17,800
