6
00:00:22,800 --> 00:00:26,500
But does it generalise?

7
00:00:26,800 --> 00:00:32,500
Walk-forward — replay best on held-out data.
Pearson 0.879.

8
00:00:32,800 --> 00:00:36,500
KC-4 threshold 0.50, declared up-front.
Cannot be lowered after seeing the score.

9
00:00:36,800 --> 00:00:42,500
All four kill criteria PASS.
Train-rank predicts test-rank. Ship.

10
00:00:42,800 --> 00:00:48,500
Fractal vise refines further.
alpha 0.5 → 0.4375. Same discipline, finer grid.

11
00:00:49,000 --> 00:00:55,500
Works for any CalibrableTarget.
Trading. Prompts. Any hyperparameter.

